# Code Owners for Eiku Game Engine
#
# This file defines who is responsible for reviewing changes to specific parts
# of the Eiku codebase. Code owners are automatically requested for review when
# someone opens a pull request that modifies code in a directory they own.
#
# More information: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global fallback - applies to everything unless more specific rules below
